        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Enhancing Emergency and Retirement Savings Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill permits penalty-free distributions, up to $1,000, from tax-exempt retirement plans for emergency personal expenses, limited to one distribution in a calendar year. The bill allows repayment to plans of such distributions over a three-year period.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
